review_text:
This game just got released and I had to. I really had to. (An addictive for cats here) A short, delightful Christmas experience by Travellin Cats. 

PROS:
- Simple, cute, delightful experience;
- Cats' meows are done by humans. It's so cute and silly!;
- Nice music;
- Hidden secrets in the environment;
- Main game + Timed game.

CONS:
- None.

I recommend this game to all of my friends that love Hidden Object games and cats!
